               stealing, on the <rs id="t18250915-250-cd1342" type="crimeDate">23d of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250915-250-off1341 t18250915-250-cd1342"></join>, at <placeName id="t18250915-250-crimeloc1343">St. James, Westminster</placeName>
